# thoth_evidence_backfill

Triggers `POST /:tenant-id/governance/evidence/thoth/backfill` and stores execution stats.

## Example Usage

```terraform
resource "thoth_evidence_backfill" "r8" {
  trigger                = "2026-05-r8"
  limit                  = 200
  include_blocked_events = true
  dry_run                = false
  integration_id         = "thoth-runtime"
}
```
